column_description: The ID of the participant who performed the song, referencing the 'id' column in the 'participants' table
The ID of the song performed by the participant, referencing the 'id' column in the 'songs' table
A score representing the quality of the participant's voice during the performance, measured on a scale (e.g., 0 to 10)
A score representing the participant's ability to maintain rhythm and tempo during the performance, measured on a scale (e.g., 0 to 10)
A score representing the participant's stage presence and overall performance charisma, measured on a scale (e.g., 0 to 10)
